---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Ultika Premium Transport"
  description="Terms of Service for Ultika Premium Transport. Read our terms and conditions for using our transportation and car rental services."
>
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' })}</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 space-y-8">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              By accessing or using Ultika's services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and all applicable laws and regulations. If you do not agree with any of these terms, you are prohibited from using our services.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">2. Services Provided</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Ultika provides the following services:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li>Airport and intercity transfers</li>
              <li>Executive transportation services</li>
              <li>Self-drive car rental</li>
              <li>Wedding and event transportation</li>
              <li>Corporate transportation solutions</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">3. Booking and Reservations</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <p><strong>3.1 Booking Process:</strong> All bookings must be made through our website, phone, or email. Reservations are subject to vehicle availability.</p>
              <p><strong>3.2 Confirmation:</strong> A booking is confirmed only when you receive a confirmation email or message from us.</p>
              <p><strong>3.3 Accuracy:</strong> You are responsible for providing accurate booking information, including pick-up location, destination, date, and time.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">4. Payment Terms</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <p><strong>4.1 Pricing:</strong> All prices are quoted in Euros (EUR) and include VAT unless otherwise stated.</p>
              <p><strong>4.2 Payment Methods:</strong> We accept cash, bank transfers, and major credit cards.</p>
              <p><strong>4.3 Deposit:</strong> A deposit may be required for certain bookings, especially for long-term rentals.</p>
              <p><strong>4.4 Additional Charges:</strong> Extra charges may apply for services such as waiting time, additional stops, highway tolls, or parking fees.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">5. Cancellation and Refund Policy</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <p><strong>5.1 Cancellation by Customer:</strong></p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-1">
                <li>Cancellations made 24+ hours before service: Full refund</li>
                <li>Cancellations made 12-24 hours before service: 50% refund</li>
                <li>Cancellations made less than 12 hours before service: No refund</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-3"><strong>5.2 Cancellation by Ultika:</strong> If we cancel your booking, you will receive a full refund or alternative arrangement at no extra cost.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">6. Driver and Vehicle Requirements</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <p><strong>6.1 For Self-Drive Rentals:</strong></p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-1">
                <li>Valid driver's license (held for minimum 2 years)</li>
                <li>Minimum age of 21 years (25 for luxury vehicles)</li>
                <li>Valid identification or passport</li>
                <li>Security deposit as specified in the rental agreement</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-3"><strong>6.2 Vehicle Condition:</strong> You must return the vehicle in the same condition as received, with a full tank of fuel.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">7. Customer Responsibilities</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">As a customer, you agree to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li>Be punctual for scheduled pick-ups</li>
              <li>Treat our vehicles and drivers with respect</li>
              <li>Not smoke in vehicles unless permitted</li>
              <li>Not transport illegal substances or items</li>
              <li>Follow all traffic laws when driving rental vehicles</li>
              <li>Report any accidents or damages immediately</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">8. Liability and Insurance</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <p><strong>8.1 Insurance Coverage:</strong> All our vehicles are fully insured for transportation services. Rental vehicles include basic insurance coverage.</p>
              <p><strong>8.2 Liability Limitations:</strong> Ultika is not liable for delays caused by traffic, weather, or circumstances beyond our control.</p>
              <p><strong>8.3 Damages:</strong> Customers are responsible for any damage to rental vehicles not covered by insurance, resulting from negligence or misuse.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">9. Force Majeure</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              We are not liable for failure to perform our obligations due to circumstances beyond our reasonable control, including but not limited to natural disasters, strikes, war, or government restrictions.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">10. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              All content on our website, including text, graphics, logos, and images, is the property of Ultika and protected by copyright laws. Unauthorized use is prohibited.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">11. Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Your use of our services is also governed by our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-[#D4AF37] hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>. We are committed to protecting your personal information in accordance with applicable data protection laws.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">12. Dispute Resolution</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Any disputes arising from these terms or our services shall be resolved through good faith negotiation. If negotiation fails, disputes shall be subject to the jurisdiction of courts in Skopje, North Macedonia.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">13. Modifications to Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting on our website. Your continued use of our services constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">14. Contact Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              For questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 space-y-2">
              <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:ultika.mk@gmail.com" class="text-[#D4AF37] hover:underline">ultika.mk@gmail.com</a></p>
              <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+38970377925" class="text-[#D4AF37] hover:underline">+389 70 377 925</a></p>
              <p class="text-gray-700"><strong>Address:</strong> Skopje, North Macedonia</p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

        <!-- Back to Home -->
        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-[#D4AF37] hover:underline">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
            </svg>
            Back to Home
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
